  "detailed_description": "Set in a cartoon world, you shoot, block and dodge your way through hordes of hilarious enemies that drive and fly around in their clunky vehicles. Steal their scrap, upgrade your skills and build a weapon so insane it just might work! How far will you get?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Built exclusively for VR, GAZZLERS will keep you on your toes as you’ll have to physically aim, block and dodge your way through waves of bullet hell goodness!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each new weapon or upgrade you find impacts your gun and your play style. Combine found parts into the ultimate weapon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/3b5b76b3259ab81f24ee8d5d9afa347a.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Game over? No problem! Every time you die, you take your scrap with you. Upgrade your skill tree, and try again, stronger than ever!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CHALLENGES ADDED: Complete your daily and weekly challenges and earn even more scrap!<br></li><li>DIFFICULTIES ADDED: Push yourself like never before with our new Nightmare mode and rise through the ranks in our leaderboards!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/7ffd4c169a0b2d4428f687a4dbc11867.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Co-created by Stijn Mommen.",
  "about_the_game": "Set in a cartoon world, you shoot, block and dodge your way through hordes of hilarious enemies that drive and fly around in their clunky vehicles. Steal their scrap, upgrade your skills and build a weapon so insane it just might work! How far will you get?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/62e32aeb9213363737a33c0b7b3adfdb.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Built exclusively for VR, GAZZLERS will keep you on your toes as you’ll have to physically aim, block and dodge your way through waves of bullet hell goodness!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.poster.avif?t=1726409526\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.webm?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/8ddefcade4ef44f8ab93fb383775321b.mp4?t=1726409526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each new weapon or upgrade you find impacts your gun and your play style. Combine found parts into the ultimate weapon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707620/extras/